column5: That’s pretty much the same as me. After a couple of failed attempts I made a promise to my 6 year old daughter and that’s the only thing that keeps me going now. It’s a personal inner fight I have to deal with everyday but it’s better to fight for a promise to her as it would be easy if I made a promise to myself to fall.
